726896f-a.title: Queens: Home Lawn Street - Charlecote Ridge
726896f-a.text:
Home Lawn Street, at Charlecote Ridge, showing two
views of the surrounding area. Grand Central Parkway was
later cut through at the intersection of the two thorough-
fares.
April 6, 1927
Views 1 and 2
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
